{"tid":362210,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［Switch/3DS討論|Overcooked|DQ11|Splatoon2|MHXX|（55）","createTime":"2017-08-16T18:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T03:28:57.000Z","uid":119778,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ddd6e8141f982f9f1ef3ef025bc7060d2640a7","tid":362210,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T18:09:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch Online App開放下載 (香港未有)</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg&h=467237b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApp功能<br />\n1.同唔同遊戲會有連動要素, 例如Splatoon2, 透過個app可以睇到自己嘅對戰相關數據同買裝<br />\n2. 可以進行語音通話<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg&h=91a4ea8a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Uniqlo UTGP'17 x Nintendo 得奬設計公佈</strong></span></span><br />\n5月26日公開發售<br />\n詳情: <a href=\"http://www.uniqlo.com/utgp2017/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uniqlo.com%2Futgp2017%2Fhk%2F&d=utbgAvDZuwliJpfUEHSaYBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=eec6cbe5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.uniqlo.com/utgp2017/hk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/NXBYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNXBYz.jpg&h=d6142c09&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch會員服務2018年開始收費 </span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBTWWkfWAAAbXXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDBTWWkfWAAAbXXD.jpg&h=d41ddfcd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\n服務內容:<br />\n1. 網絡對戰, 直至2018年服務開始前用家可免費使用此功能<br />\n2. 使用網絡對戰開房/配對及語音通話App, 其測試版已開放下載<br />\n3. 可以遊玩<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">追加網絡功能</span></strong>的&quot;任天堂經典遊戲&quot;, 遊戲數目會不斷增加, 首批已知遊戲包括 「Super Mario Bros. 3」, 「Balloon Fight」, 「Dr. Mario」<br />\n4. eShop 遊戲優惠<br />\n<br />\n收費: <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每年</span> 19.99USD/ 2400YEN (<span style=\"color: red;\">約港幣$160</span>)<br />\n可只購買1或3個月會員資格, 惟其價格亦較昂貴<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>常見問題</strong></span></span></div><br />\n <br />\nQ: 駁上電視玩 畫面會定格/疾, 但係手提mode又無事?<br />\nA: 有批機出事, 請致電香港任天堂安排更換<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=utbgAvDZuwliJpfUEHSaYBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=616a22c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 孖車/炸彈人/ARMS/Splatoon2等網絡對戰遊戲online玩唔到?<br />\nA: 港服未開, 去<a href=\"https://accounts.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.nintendo.com&d=utbgAvDZuwliJpfUEHSaYBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=29451269\" target=\"_blank\">https://accounts.nintendo.com</a>轉region做日本/美國<br />\n <br />\nQ: 電量顯示有問題? 叉到100%熄機再開無左十幾%? 叉到XX%之後唔識再上?<br />\nA: Bug黎, 要等更新解決, 唔好熄機就得 (Sleep mode方便好多添啦) <br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon 連接有問題/ 用用下無反應?<br />\nA: 可以試下撳實JoyCon側邊個Sync掣2秒<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點揀叉電器/USB-C 線?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5oXEONa.png&d=utbgAvDZuwliJpfUEHSaYBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=91d92328\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon手帶調轉插點算?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7bfhKo7dqIo&d=utbgAvDZuwliJpfUEHSaYBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=27670c3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 點連5Ghz WiFi?<br />\nA: Set 個WiFi Channel去36-64 or 100-140之間<br />\n <br />\nQ: 點連啲要打ac pw 登入嘅WIFI?<br />\nA: 無解<br />\n<br />\nQ: 部機黑畫面/定咗格/撳電源掣冇反應<br />\nA: 長撳開關掣十二秒<br />\n <br />\nQ: 要keep咩先有保養?<br />\nA: 1. 需維修的主機及配件 2. 主機外箱　 3. 印有銷售店舖名稱或蓋印之購買收據　4. 主機包裝內之香港原裝行貨保固證 <a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=utbgAvDZuwliJpfUEHSaYBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=616a22c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 孖車8/Zelda咩版先有英文/日文?<br />\nA: 跟你部機嘅語言(可以入設定轉)，無中文<br />\n <br />\nQ: Switch行版/日版/美版有咩分別?<br />\nA: 行版有保養同香港用嘅三腳火牛(不過任何版本都係用國際牛)，其他一樣，內置多國語言(無中文)<br />\n <br />\nQ: Switch有無鎖區?<br />\nA: 無，eShop 分區跟 ac，一機可同時登入 8 個 ac <br />\n <br />\nQ: 點解話入唔到eShop?話shop not available?<br />\nA: 港服未開，建議開多個美國/日本ac 入 美/日eShop啦<br />\n <br />\nQ: 左Joy-Con出事?<br />\nA: Joy-Con連接/同步問題解決方法:<br />\n更新Switch系統後插左右Joy-Cons落Switch本體再重開機<span style=\"color: red;\">或</span>可解決Joy-Con連接/同步問題<br />\n亦可嘗試入手掣setting disconnect joycon 再重新開機<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都係唔得嘅可以致電香港任天堂安排測試&amp;更換</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=utbgAvDZuwliJpfUEHSaYBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=616a22c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a>"},{"pid":"312b2a9ace9512f1ddaac92f8ac921fa12e9dbe5","tid":362210,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T19:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fa51d39bd67e65ec69e4112b4b2eeebbe67172","tid":362210,"uid":36341,"like":0,"d