 />\n之後自己後來買多部用翻同一個ac 有無辦法down翻落嚟新機到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢而家得個purchased字係到 想再買到唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb67fcb70acf7bab3d0e7b5faa7221542485465","tid":362210,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係女朋友部switch到買咗overcooked<br />\n之後自己後來買多部用翻同一個ac 有無辦法down翻落嚟新機到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢而家得個purchased字係到 想再買到唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係佢部機解除左你個ac未<br />\nbtw佢會冇得玩"}]}